# HTTP and www redirects — enforce the canonical https://edunancial.com origin.
# DO NOT add a "/* /index.html 200" SPA catch-all here.  This site uses
# Next.js App Router via @netlify/plugin-nextjs; there is no index.html in
# the publish directory, and such a rule would silently rewrite every request
# (including POST /api/admin/content/upload/presign) to /index.html, causing
# Netlify to return a 404 HTML page instead of the expected JSON API response.
http://edunancial.com/* https://edunancial.com/:splat 301!
http://www.edunancial.com/* https://edunancial.com/:splat 301!
https://www.edunancial.com/* https://edunancial.com/:splat 301!
